              "free_text": [
                "",
                " Elastic scattering data.",
                " For the present data, novel analysis procedure was",
                "applied, allowing cross sections for inelastic neutron",
                "scattering to be extracted from the same data sets.",
                "For attenuation and multiple neutron scattering in the",
                "scattering targets based on Monte Carlo codes.",
                "Response correction."
              ]
            }
